title: This is What I Call Minimal 80s! Vol. 11
description:
Part 11 of these compilations which includes some great obscure songs. What I love about minimal synth is the fact that they were created with the least musical euipments and little or no production, sometimes from a little basement suit. That's why they sound so natural and genuine.
